<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Nov 2021 14:25:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>全新 Kia Niro 將於 25 日現身　預計採用更大膽設計</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/22/kia-teases-second-generation-niro/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=kia-teases-second-generation-niro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 22 Nov 2021 14:25:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[kia]]></category><category><![CDATA[SUV]]></category><category><![CDATA[電動車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1072632</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>電動車熱潮下，韓國車廠也沒有缺席，Kia 就有推出了幾款電動車，最近更預告新一代的電動 SUV Niro 將會在 11 月 25 日正式亮相。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>電動車熱潮下，韓國車廠也沒有缺席，Kia 就有推出了幾款電動車，最近更預告新一代的電動 SUV Niro 將會在 11 月 25 日正式亮相。<br /><span id="more-1072632"></span></p><p>Kia 公佈了幾張預告圖，雖然都只可以看到大概的輪廓和大燈設計，但已經可以大概理解其設計概念會沿用 2019 年公開的 HabaNiro 概念車的「Opposites United」設計語言，有更加大膽前衛的線條，提升其科技感。從圖片看來它將不會採用「鉸剪式」車門，繼續是傳統四門設計，但其他部分依然有強烈風格。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_81517"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D7IJCPkhXiA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>全新 Niro 將會在 11 月 25 日的首爾車展正式亮相，屆時就可以看到其真面目了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1072633" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1072634" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1072635" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/2022-kia-niro-teaser-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://insideevs.com/news/549524/kia-teases-second-generation-niro/">InsideEVs</a></p>
